Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么而生下来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  回答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:46.92,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:51.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}失控
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座小镇里  有着充满了谜团的杀人集团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在此居住有什么问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆就回旧市好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚他绝不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且是先给您一个忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再给我们一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我们都没有过…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们应该已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年比较特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们想一家人一起克服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然您这么说  那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄同学  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无变化的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平凡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总觉得发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惊吓过度了  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我提前来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  居然丢下她了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃一定生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  难道说和小铃吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  博士君有些地方还是很迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定已经惹小铃生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  博士君？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你觉得我是个麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的叔父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个中心的栉名田院长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说我是个奇怪的人什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  如果有什么话要和我说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃请假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天也精神地开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时把一诚关在家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  我们家人必须做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃也同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子说不定要不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还有胶囊什么的  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错  家人一起克服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃  你也要当心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连你也有什么事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看老哥的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿胶囊来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  你也需要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联防队那些家伙来过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  之前有说过嫦娥镇流传的都市传说的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个还有些怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在镇上的食人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病院的幽灵病房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排成队伍的红色萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响彻半夜的野兽叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些类似的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在镇上的食人鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是这个城镇里住着怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们会袭击人这样的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据传闻怪物半夜在镇上徘徊寻找食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有人烟的地方袭击人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样袭击的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是从人的口中直接吸取生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得像是猎奇电影一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有些事想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一个传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市传说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着大镰刀的少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  昨晚真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个少女袭击人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是想去报警的  但却没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上又去了现场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事件的痕迹却完全不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  拿着大镰刀的少女的传闻什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的都市传说听过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个没有听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是这事听起来挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为博士君来说  算是不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不错什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这样的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是「有其父必有其子」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…这可不是我瞎编的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不过还是继续说给我听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好再说说那个拿着大镰刀的少女的角色特点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让故事更有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  小铃怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前都不怎么请假的  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去时我去看望一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  工作有进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  走三步退二步的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒退怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  最近遇到难关了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  这里的传说中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关于拿着大镰刀的少女的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话去问同班同学那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  小要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她擅长的领域吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学也说不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我更不可能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但姑且会调查一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到哥哥收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  今天不是麻奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是替过你一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘记了  是是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找1年前遗弃在南极的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对饥饿的两条猛犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能活下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影  结局——南极物语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近日即将公开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完电影后的用餐可选择离本院徒步1分钟的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店  艾特兰泽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店  艾  特  兰  泽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔~ 八朔~ 嫦娥的八朔~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸呀~ 酸呀~ 呀呀呀呀呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去丢下垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说会从人的口中吸取生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被杀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为会这样  我们才忠告你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁？  放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你安分点  我们便不会动粗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我们走一趟么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和…  摘花前辈他一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据戒律  摘花一诚先生他应当很快就会受到制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且  你也已经不再是迄今为止的那个你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是爽毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么爽的事  为什么我一直以来都得忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝过了这味道  就再也回不去原先的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回你个头！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠天之神  除之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(326,434)\fs24}狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈他…  怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有些疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样根本就无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联防队町田先生叫我传个话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摘花一诚变成「神人」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石我木雅美  请叔父大人处置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那边  明天就由我亲自来说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也挺不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她  今天也休息么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说  哥你被她甩了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不走的话  可要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去叫下她？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她真不太舒服  还在睡的话  可就打扰她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此  你也别再护着一诚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会说出那么冷淡的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是一家人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不想连你也一并失去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶囊的事应该是机密事项
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是怎么查出来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这世上  知晓消息的人只要超过了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便不可能保密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打的是什么算盘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一早就说了的么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想助院长您一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  就像你们医生为了解患者的病情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要借助病历卡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的新药  也得靠着数据来开发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:19:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就没有联系过你么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她家  你也没去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  没去成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也精神地开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  安静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐回座位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  摘花  正好迟到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可让我担心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就先点名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  感冒好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…  昨天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈他搬家了…  这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.84,0:22:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:18.06,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:18.06,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘怀  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:28.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが信じた愛の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:28.76,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信之情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:35.01,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱きしめた夜には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:35.01,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拥夜入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:37.87,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影が月でなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:37.87,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影非月  月非影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:41.25,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繰り返す罪には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:41.25,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:49.80,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}戸惑いの月が満ちる　融ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:49.80,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}盈惑月  消无痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:56.64,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いくつものこころが　君を縛るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:56.64,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心结若缚君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:23:07.25,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}堕ちて行く決意が許されるまで　愛なのと信じたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:23:07.25,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}则深信此爱  直至神允  坠天之志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:14.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}かすかな声手繰り寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:14.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}细语声中忆往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:20.37,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}交わる闇の調べ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:20.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱恨交织暗之乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:27.14,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繋いでいく　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:27.14,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此相思  永相连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:37.82,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが夢見た時の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:37.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}入我梦  彼情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六心乱极
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃若闇虚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔之力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔香里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望镇邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那未曾被我接受的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那难以令我理解的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么办…  怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来  我还是什么也办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  恋
